OL,3,CWidow of stabbing victim condemns
OL,4,C'zombie' knife compensation scheme
OL,6,FA woman whose husband was murdered in
OL,7,Ftheir home by teenagers armed with a
OL,8,Fso-called "zombie" knife has branded a
OL,9,Fgovernment scheme to compensate
OL,10,Fsuppliers "ridiculous".
OL,12,FLouise Dyson was at home in
OL,13,FHuddersfield with Khalfan Seif and
OL,14,Ftheir three young children when a gang
OL,15,Fburst into their home demanding money
OL,16,Fin January 2023.
OL,18,FShe managed to escape with the
OL,19,Fchildren, but Mr Seif, 33, was fatally
OL,20,Fstabbed.
