OL,3,CWidow of stabbing victim condemns
OL,4,C'zombie' knife compensation scheme
OL,6,FNow, 18 months on, a ban on zombie-
OL,7,Fstyle knives and machetes will come
OL,8,Finto force next week.
OL,10,FThe government is offering businesses
OL,11,Fthat stock them #10 a weapon to
OL,12,Fsurrender them.
OL,14,FMs Dyson told ITV News: "That's just
OL,15,Fridiculous. How can you money off
OL,16,Fsomething that's killing people. I
OL,17,Fdon't get it."
OL,19,FWhat is a zombie knife?
