OL,3,CWidow of stabbing victim condemns
OL,4,C'zombie' knife compensation scheme
OL,6,FSo-called zombie knives vary in size
OL,7,Fand shape.
OL,9,FBut they are legally defined in the UK
OL,10,Fas having a cutting edge, a serrated
OL,11,Fedge and images or words (whether on
OL,12,Fthe blade or handle) that suggest that
OL,13,Fit is to be used for the purpose of
OL,14,Fviolence.
OL,16,FAccording to a freedom of information
OL,17,Frequest, West Yorkshire Police
OL,18,Frecorded 1,004 crimes in 2023
OL,19,Finvolving zombie knives or machetes -
OL,20,Fup from 732 the year before.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
