OL,3,CWidow of stabbing victim condemns
OL,4,C'zombie' knife compensation scheme
OL,6,FRecalling the night her husband was
OL,7,Fkilled, Ms Dyson said her first
OL,8,Finstinct when the attackers broke in
OL,9,Fto their home in Springdale Avenue was
OL,10,Fto protect her children.
OL,12,FShe said: "All I was thinking was I
OL,13,Fneed to get my kids to safety. That
OL,14,Fwas literally all that was going
OL,15,Fthrough my head."
OL,17,F"As I've got across the road, Khalfans
OL,18,Fcome out. He was obviously in a really
OL,19,Fbad way and saying he'd been stabbed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
