OL,3,CWidow of stabbing victim condemns
OL,4,C'zombie' knife compensation scheme
OL,6,F"He was saying he was going to die.
OL,7,FFrom the state he was in I already
OL,8,Fknew that that was it. But it was
OL,9,Fhorrible."
OL,11,FMr Seif had suffered a fatal wound to
OL,12,Fthe stomach.JIn October last year,
OL,13,Fbrothers Amaan and Sahil Ansar, who
OL,14,Fwere both 19, were found guilty of his
OL,15,Fmurder and jailed for life.
OL,17,FA third teenager, 19-year-old Wahaab
OL,18,FSaif, was found guilty of manslaughter.
