OL,3,CWidow of stabbing victim condemns
OL,4,C'zombie' knife compensation scheme
OL,6,FMs Dyson added: "The way knife crime
OL,7,Fis now, I'm terrified for my kids when
OL,8,Fthey grow up.
OL,10,F"My children will grow up without a
OL,11,Ffather because of knife crime."
OL,13,FZombie knives will be added to the
OL,14,Flist of banned weapons which already
OL,15,Fincludes butterfly knives, Samurai
OL,16,Fswords and push daggers.
