OL,4,C'zombie' knife compensation scheme
OL,6,FPeople are being urged to hand over
OL,7,Fthe weapons at designated police
OL,8,Fstations as part of an amnesty scheme
OL,9,Fbefore the ban comes into force on 24
OL,10,FSeptember.
OL,12,FUK company, Sporting Wholesale, which
OL,13,Fowns the firm Anglo Arms, has handed
OL,14,Fover 35 thousand zombie knives.
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Deputy Mayor for
OL,17,FPolicing and Crime, Alison Lowe
OL,18,Fbelieves businesses in possession of
OL,19,Fthese weapons should not be "rewarded".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
