OL,4,C'zombie' knife compensation scheme
OL,6,FShe added: "These businesses ought not
OL,7,Fto exist in the first place because
OL,8,Fthey are purveyors of death.
OL,10,F"Why would we need big hunting knives,
OL,11,Fzombie knives, machetes."
OL,13,FITV News has approached Sporting
OL,14,FWholesale for comment.
OL,16,FThe Home Office said the compensation
OL,17,Fscheme was designed under the previous
OL,18,Fgovernment, adding in a statement:
OL,19,F"Tackling knife crime is a moral
OL,20,Fmission upon all in society.
